[I] Python library to determine platform-specific system directories

[T] platformdirs is a Python package for determining platform-specific
[T] directories (e.g. user data, config, cache, logs). Handles the differences
[T] between macOS, Windows, Linux/Unix, and Android so you don't have to.

[U] https://github.com/platformdirs/platformdirs

